  <brief_title>Accuracy of RTE for Evaluating Hepatic Fibrosis in Chronic Hepatitis: a Prospective Multicenter Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Accuracy of Real-time Tissue Elastography for Evaluating Hepatic Fibrosis in Chronic Hepatitis: a Prospective Multicenter Study.</official_title>
