  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Our study is a prospective multicenter research and the aim is to explore a variety of
      suitable evaluation indicators and criteria for diagnosis of diffuse liver fibrosis, to get
      the corresponding diagnosis threshold, with the domestic common pathological S stages as the
      gold standard.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
